body:
Follow the steps to [Create a MongoDB Vector Search Index](avs-create-index) for the `hr_database.employees`
namespace. Name the index `vector_index` and specify
the following index definition:

```json
{
  "fields": [
    {
      "numDimensions": 1024,
      "path": "embedding",
      "similarity": "cosine",
      "type": "vector"
    }
  ]
}
```
